Due to grater detail and map information, the 2014 BMW Navigation Maps are separated in two (2) DVD discs:

2014 BMW - North American Map DVD - 'HIGH' compatible with the following vehicles with trunk loading Navigation Systems:
- 3-Series (E46, MK4)
- 5-Series (E39 ( SA 609 ), MK4)
- 7-Series (E65 ( SA 609 ), E66 ( SA 609 ))
- X3 (E83)
- X5 (E53)
- Z4 (E85 ( SA 609 ))
- Z8 (E52)	


Installation directions:

Burn ISOs using ImgBurn or similar program. 

It's recommended to burn at the slowest speed possible because the DVD drives in the navigation unit can be a little touchy.
